Target Hardware
  Raspberry Pi Zero W
  BME280 sensor (temperature, pressure, humidity)

Server
  Apache Server (redirect port 80 to 443, reverse proxy 443 --> 8080)
  Postgres DB
    location
    measurement
  Dockerized Node/TypeScript app
    embedded Express server hosts API/UI on port 8080
  Python bme280.py script in cronjob (every minute)
    writes sensor data to /tmp/sensor

UI
  Bootstrap styles
  Fetch XHR 
    get data from API every minute

Docker Container
  docker build -t wx-station .
  (tag/push/pull)
  docker run --restart=always -d \
    --network=host \
    --env DB_USER=user \
    --env DB_DATABASE=db \
    --env DB_PASSWORD=pass \
    --mount type=bind,source=/tmp,target=/tmp \
    -p 8080:8080 wx-station npm run server

